{"tid":1034153,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完呢個post 你諗起既第一個人 請你捉緊佢並好好對待佢","createTime":"2019-02-23T16:30:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T04:41:56.000Z","uid":98700,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b7f76aa42709cec4e9344bbb0ff7e5954afe3e76","tid":1034153,"uid":98700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T16:30:52.000Z","msg":"有感而發<br />\n<br />\n佢會幫你打點日常生活，你有咩行程、有咩要做、要準備啲咩，佢會提你。<br />\n佢當你係佢家人咁濟，成個媽咪咁，提你著多件衫，唔好餓親，提你早啲訓，傷身呀。<br />\n佢會將你所講既野擺係心，可能你只係輕輕提過，佢都記到實一實，甚至可能連你都唔記得，佢都竟然記得。<br />\n佢知道就算你唔鐘意佢，佢仍然默默付出。<br />\n<br />\n冇一個人會咁義無反顧，唯獨佢。<br />\n<br />\n佢可能只想得到你既認同。<br />\n<br />\n睇到呢到，你諗起邊個？<br />\n<br />\n冇人會無理由咁對你好，唔係一定㗎，佢對你咁好，你有冇感恩呀？你明知佢咩意思，如果你都有同樣意思，你開聲啦，唔好錯過任何時間，火花不等人。<br />\n<br />\n同佢講聲我愛你啦。<br />\n<br />\nFf....."},{"pid":"4591d86807218d526d4957d0fa0c4d0d379eceb6","tid":1034153,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T16:31:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ccd1c5da6d28fc9450830baa065861e06fb004","tid":1034153,"uid":18411,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T16:36:29.000Z","msg":"啊媽，多謝你啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e31171e2214e54b0a3b067a7d7dad3c696e9403","tid":1034153,"uid":165510,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T17:29:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5596b6ae4ffe4fd2f5534266b680521217f35c91","tid":1034153,"uid":173326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T19:08:48.000Z","msg":"睇完，冇呢個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1db67721cde73951bb28fff8dee0a9bdfbaa49e2","tid":1034153,"uid":11760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T19:12:17.000Z","msg":"睇完 諗唔起<br />\n唯有多謝自己"},{"pid":"923b0d5035e3eb